				<div>
					<h2>Average Traffic in KBps by network interfaces over last 24 hours in a line chart by server names (auto span definition using custom macro)</h2>
					<pre>eventtype=nmon:performance type=NET frameID=$frameID$ hostname=$hostname$
| timechart `inline_customspan` avg(value) AS value by device</pre>
				</div>

				<div>
					<div class="cat_title">
